From: Tino Mettler <tino@tikei.de>
Date: Thu, 23 Oct 2014 11:37:22 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Fix undefined reference to symbol
 '__cxa_free_exception@@CXXABI_1.3'
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Fix a linker error ld: /«PKGBUILDDIR»/lib/db_key.o: undefined reference to symbol '__cxa_free_exception@@CXXABI_1.3'
by using a patch from YunQiang Su.

Closes: #713672, #762419
Thanks: YunQiang Su <wzssyqa@gmail.com>
---
 configure | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/configure b/configure
index 29ee96c..013a52e 100755
--- a/configure
+++ b/configure
@@ -189,7 +189,7 @@ if test "$#" = "0" && test -z "$DARWIN" && test -z "$QTDIR" && \
    pkg-config QtGui openssl --libs >/dev/null;
 then
   CF="`pkg-config QtGui openssl --cflags`"
-  LIBS="`pkg-config QtGui openssl --libs` -lltdl"
+  LIBS="`pkg-config QtGui openssl --libs` -lltdl -lstdc++"
 else
   by_hand=true
 fi
